title: How Diet Culture is Destroying You with Abbey Sharp
description: Hey ya'll! In today's episode, we have nutritionist, Abbey Sharp. She will be speaking about the old and new diet cultures and how they impact you and you diet decisions. She will also lay out the reality of a healthy diet and lifestyle.  Abbey's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/abbeyskitchen/ --- Send in a voice message: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/message Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/support
